        "text": "I have adapted our \"Stealth\" pitch to fit their strict format while keeping the \"Nerd Bait\" hook.\nStealth PropTech Startup | Boston, MA (or Remote) | Founding Full-Stack Engineer | CONTRACT TO HIRE | Competitive Market Rate + Equity\nWe are looking for a \"Mad Scientist\" engineer to build a living, gamified dashboard that disrupts a massive legacy industry (Consumer Logistics/Real Estate).\nThe Stack: React, Next.js, Supabase, Node.js. (Bonus: Framer Motion/GSAP).\nThe Project:\nThis isn't a CRUD app. It is a \"Command Center\" that feels like a video game. It features a dynamic \"AI Companion\" (Nook) that actively coaches users through complex financial and logistical phases. We need someone who can take a \"Frankenstein\" MVP concept and turn it into a high-performance, secure, living organism.\nAbout You:\n* You treat your IDE like a video game.\n* You obsess over micro-interactions and \"game feel.\"\n* You want to be Employee #1 on a product that solves a universal anxiety point for 40k+ users in Boston alone.\nThe Deal:\n* Mode: Contract-to-hire. We start with the MVP build (paid project). If you survive the mission, you become the Founding Engineer.\n* Culture: No Jira. No PMs. Just code and shipping.\nTo Apply:\nEmail me at jobroplus@gmail.com\nDo NOT send a resume. Send ONE link to the coolest/weirdest thing you have ever built. Show me code with a soul.",
